---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
---
{% from "partials/committee-card.njk" import card %}
{% set openList = committees.committees | openCommittees %}
{% set openSeats = committees.committees | totalOpenSeats %}

<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">{{ site.college }} · {{ site.academicYear }}</p>
  <h1>Help shape UCF. Represent CECS on a Faculty Senate committee.</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    Faculty Senate committees decide on curriculum, budget, research policy, promotion
    and tenure, technology, and more. When CECS shows up, engineering and computer
    science perspectives shape those decisions. Browse the committees below and add
    your name — most ask for only a few hours a semester.
  </p>
  <p class="hero-actions">
    <a class="btn btn-large" href="{{ '/signup/' | url }}">Volunteer now</a>
    <a class="btn btn-large btn-ghost" href="{{ '/committees/' | url }}">Browse committees</a>
  </p>
  <p class="hero-stat">
    {% if openSeats %}
      <strong>{{ committees.committees | length }}</strong> committees ·
      <strong>{{ openSeats }}</strong> open CECS seat{{ 's' if openSeats != 1 }} across
      <strong>{{ openList | length }}</strong> committee{{ 's' if openList | length != 1 }}
    {% else %}
      <strong>{{ committees.committees | length }}</strong> committees ·
      every CECS seat filled for {{ site.academicYear }}
    {% endif %}
  </p>
</section>

<section class="band">
  <h2>Why serve?</h2>
  <div class="cols-3">
    <div>
      <h3>Have a voice</h3>
      <p>Curriculum, calendar, budget, IT, and P&amp;T policy all run through these committees. Representation means CECS is in the room.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>Low lift, real impact</h3>
      <p>Most committees meet monthly or a few times a semester. It's one of the highest-leverage forms of university service.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>Build your record</h3>
      <p>University-level service strengthens your annual review and promotion case while growing your network across colleges.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
  </div>
  <ol class="steps">
    <li><strong>Browse</strong> the committees and find one that fits your interests and schedule.</li>
    <li><strong>Volunteer</strong> with the short form — pick one or more committees.</li>
    <li><strong>Get matched.</strong> The CECS rep coordinates nominations with the Faculty Senate Committee on Committees.</li>
    <li><strong>Stay informed.</strong> Check the <a href="{{ '/updates/' | url }}">Updates</a> page through the year for news and openings.</li>
  </ol>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>Committees needing CECS reps</h2>
    <a class="link" href="{{ '/committees/' | url }}">See all {{ committees.committees | length }} →</a>
  </div>
  {% if openList | length %}
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for committee in openList | limit(6) %}
        {{ card(committee, signups, committeeDetails) }}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <p class="empty">Every CECS seat is filled for {{ site.academicYear }} — thank you! You can still <a href="{{ '/signup/' | url }}">register or update your interest</a> to be first in line for future vacancies.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>
